{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "埃利亚斯 第2话 歌声传达的感情",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "咦？\\n让埃利亚斯给我帮忙？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。想让他体验一下\\n这里的各种事物。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "毕竟这城里各式各样的工作\\n做得最多的就是库菈乌了。可以吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我知道了。有人能来帮忙，\\n我倒是求之不得。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "请、请多关照。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不过既然要做，\\n就要接受我的严格训练。\\n请你做好思想准备。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "咦？训练？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "埃利亚斯！\\n接下来该洗衣服了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "洗衣服要手脚麻利！\\n毕竟能晾衣服的时间有限。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "好、好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "埃利亚斯！\\n接下来该缝补衣服了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "好、好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "埃利亚斯！\\n接下来该打扫卫生了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "好、好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "库、库菈乌好厉害啊……\\n各种事都能麻利地搞定……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "可是做这些事\\n真的有助于唱歌吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊，埃利亚斯。\\n我要去准备晚饭了，\\n来帮个我打下手吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "好、好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "洋葱要切成小块。\\n没错没错……你切得不错嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "切好洋葱之后，\\n把它倒进这两口锅里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "好的……咦？\\n库菈乌，为什么有两口锅啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "要做的是同一道菜吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嗯，这是为了做出不同的口味。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "不同的口味？\\n明明是同一道菜啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是的。因为兰扎卜口味比较重，\\n而埃尔菲莉丝喜欢清淡的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "所以要配合他们的喜好，\\n做出不同的味道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "这算什么啊。\\n那两个人也太任性了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "他们没有任性。\\n是我自己特意这么做的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "我不懂……\\n明明照着菜谱做\\n就一定会好吃啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "那样不行吗？\\n库菈乌你忙前忙后\\n已经够累的了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "呵呵，你是在担心我？\\n还挺温柔的嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "才、才没有……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这看起来的确\\n像是在自讨苦吃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "但如果这么做\\n能让吃的人感到高兴，\\n对我来说就不算是吃苦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "让吃的人感到高兴……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嗯。如果吃饭时有很多自己爱吃的饭菜，\\n你也会开心吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "谁都会这样吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "没错。\\n能吃到爱吃的饭菜，谁都会开心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "所以即使多费些工夫，\\n我也想满足他们的口味。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "按照菜谱做\\n可能也会好吃……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "可是既然要做，自然是希望\\n让别人得到最大的满足吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "最大的……满足……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "唱歌不一样吗？\\n唱歌难道不是希望\\n观众们能获得最大的享受吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "那个……没错。\\n我想让人们听到最棒的歌声。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "唱出打动观众的歌声……\\n我为了实现这个目标而拼命练习。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "按照乐谱，分毫不差地……\\n可这就像是完全按照菜谱做饭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "并不是说\\n按照菜谱做就是错的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "只是如果不能让对方感动，\\n那就算按照菜谱做也没有意义。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "好啦好啦。别在那发呆了，\\n赶快把剩下的做完吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "我开动了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢，今天的汤格外好喝啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "啊，真的呢。真好喝。\\n清淡的口感真不错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "合你们的胃口就好，\\n今天是埃利亚斯和我一起做的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喔～埃利亚斯吗？\\n干得不错嘛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "居然还会做饭，真厉害。\\n谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "啊，呃、嗯……\\n不客气……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "呵呵，能让大家满意真是太好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "基本上都是库菈乌做的，\\n我有资格接受大家的感谢吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这种时候你就坦率地\\n接受大家的好意吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你看，\\n大家都吃得津津有味呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "嗯，是啊。\\n兰扎卜都已经在添饭了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "饭菜不是做完就结束了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我们还应该好好确认\\n包含在饭菜中的感情\\n是否传达给了对方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "感情是否传达给了对方……\\n我从来没有考虑过……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "我满脑子都是怎么唱好歌，\\n从没想过观众的感受……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "库菈乌，要是有什么\\n我能帮上忙的事，请一定要告诉我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110303_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃利亚斯",
            "context": "我想向你学习\\n如何向对方传达自己的感情。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "当然可以。\\n让我们一起努力吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}